Descriptions.Description:
By car
•leave the A22 Modena-Brennero motorway from the exit TRENTO CENTRO; 
•immediately after the barrier, take the first turn on the right and follow the signs for Monte Bondone (strada statale 45 bis towards Riva del Garda); 
•after almost 1 km, ignore a first sign indicating Monte Bondone on the left hand side and keep heading straight on the statale (main road); 
•having covered other 2km and passed a tunnel, turn right towards Monte Bondone-Sopramonte; 
•drive through the village Sopramonte (here you'll find the last petrol station), and keep going up-hill for more or less 15 km (Candriai, Vaneze, Norge are some of the places you'll meet on your way). 
•As soon as you get in Vason (1650m) the Hotel Montana will be visible on the right hand side of the main road.

